{"tid":1499821,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"只要夠人，香港人可以海外建城市","createTime":"2019-08-24T01:23:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-24T02:29:49.000Z","uid":30561,"like":17,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"577acbdc16783ca0fbc89bcab484d2cbb8b19588","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:23:29.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>新加坡人 同 美國加州機構 合作 建立<span style=\"color: red;\">首個「漂浮國家」</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">（新加坡人做到香港人一定做得到）</span><br />\n<br />\n全球很多城市面對土地問題，各地政府千方百計想解決，有科學家近年提出建立「漂浮國家」，讓人以海為家，甚至在<span style=\"color: red;\">大海上立國</span>。<br />\n<br />\n全球首個漂浮國家，預計2022年將在太平洋的法屬玻里尼西亞建成，<span style=\"color: red;\">會有自己的政府，更有自己的加密貨幣</span>。這種漂浮國家，有望成為現代人心目中的烏托邦？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9cpEvArWCAA&amp;feature=youtu.be\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D9cpEvArWCAA%26feature%3Dyoutu.be&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=973c3c69\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=9cpEvArWCAA&amp;feature=youtu.be</a><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">香港不單止要面對2047嘅政治問題還有2050年嘅水位上升嘅氣候問題。</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>自設貨幣的自由之都</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n來自哥倫比亞的政治科學家梅扎加爾恰（Nathalie Mezza-Garcia）為計劃的核心成員。她形容自己為「海洋傳教士」（seavangelesse），十分讚成遷居至浮島：「當首個浮島順利建成後，我們便可以證明，興建浮島容納氣候難民的計劃是可行的。」法屬玻里尼西亞由珊瑚礁環繞，海平面上升可能會令當地失去部分土地。如浮島計劃成功，有望為太平洋的一眾島國帶來新希望。<br />\n<br />\n浮島以自給自足的形式運作，營運不會受其他政府的法律規限，且會有自己的加密貨幣Varyon。梅扎加爾恰指，浮島更可演變為商業中心，吸引創科公司到浮島發展：「浮島具穩定性，不受地緣政治、貿易問題和匯率波動影響，是孕育企業的好地方。」浮島上的政府，則只會以服務提供者的形式存在，甚至島上居民如不滿特定政府，他們可以漂浮至另一個島嶼。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RwOOuFbMn5s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DRwOOuFbMn5s&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=579f5d10\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=RwOOuFbMn5s</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">即是容許香港人在西方國家偏遠地區買地/島，建人工浮島，（假設當99+年交還 地/島比 西方政府時候，人工浮島早已經在公海建國）。。<br />\n</span></strong></span><br />\n因此以一間公司名義申請大量香港人免簽證到當地工作起人工浮島。<br />\n<br />\n將來<span style=\"color: red;\">會有自己的政府，更有自己的加密貨幣</span>，如果喜歡澳洲的，可去澳洲買地/島 起人工浮島，而香港人居住偏遠地區三年以上可取得永居權。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n各位連登仔點睇？<br />\n<br />\n海外建國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n返工不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如興趣可以加入FloatCityV出謀劃策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=66140c90\" target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URHv8qL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURHv8qL.jpg&h=5df60854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3OSsreL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OSsreL.jpg&h=0abfc092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"869f268fd3211527ab920aad78d538c2d4bb56b1","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:24:06.000Z","msg":"彈丸之地香港其實有大量嘅有錢人同埋技術人員，二百幾萬人一起做一啲嘢，投資買地，建島，錢大多用係香港工人身上，同建設新嘅社區， 如果買嗰啲小島或小魚村，係屬於美國/加拿大/英國/澳洲更加會受到軍方嘅保護， 一些西方國家有大規模接收政治難民嘅經驗 ，例如澳洲。西方有著相對優厚的移民吸引力而且比較守承諾，加上香港地有唔少人支持捐款為香港人做事，買咗嘅地方可支持建人島/社區也可以吸引大量嘅投資。 <br />\n<br />\n現在香港沒有建立信用評分制度，唔會有人因為信用評分制度影響，所以香港可以自由進出，如果俾一個有主權的人工島，就能建立屬於香港人既地方。香港不單止要面對2047嘅政治問題還有2050年嘅水位上升嘅氣候問題，重頭開始，係為香港人保留元氣，要養晦轁光，走出悲情的歷史， 唯有堅定建立一個理想的華人世界， 先可以保留正統文化，讓我地後代子孫得以挺直腰幹、開疆闢土、創造榮耀。"},{"pid":"816d58fdc567419de78d2f6ea5c5320ef94cf7fe","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:24:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/URHv8qL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FURHv8qL.jpg&h=5df60854&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/3OSsreL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3OSsreL.jpg&h=0abfc092&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"310bfd9b2ea50a42e98346844a043db7b773331f","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"其實我哋嘅目標係有<span style=\"color: red;\">主權</span>，有<span style=\"color: red;\">領土</span>。<br />\n我哋香港人唔可以再做二等公民，而家我哋係唔可以當兵，唔可以成為真正有實權既國家領導人。<br />\n<br />\n請大家推一下吧!"},{"pid":"ad7aa2ecad475f5e527849099c24086f17923761","tid":1499821,"uid":277997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n我地要趕走佢地<br />\n唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d3531789f7776a8c30c723dfa57980cb390626b","tid":1499821,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪真係起到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5a5b31822d80b5ed1895fd4a722f96616e4526b7","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1d3531789f7776a8c30c723dfa57980cb390626b","tid":1499821,"uid":280648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:58.000Z","msg":"其實係咪真係起到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:26:26.000Z","msg":"係，只要夠人，一齊發展,建設新社區"},{"pid":"f9e04338e9025fcf332032c30a529830e55084fd","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:26:43.000Z","msg":"國家定位：<br />\n<br />\n引用的文獻:蒙特維多國家權利義務公約（ <br />\nMontevideo Convention on the Rights and Duties of States）。 <br />\n此公約的第一條款說：在國際法上，一個國家應有以下資格： <br />\n1. 固定的人口（a permanent population）。 <br />\n2. 界限清楚的領土（a defined territory）。 <br />\n3. 政府（government）。 <br />\n4. 與其他國家有建立關係的能力（capacity to enter into relations with the other states）。"},{"pid":"ba49a67035a680324ecd634826992d7e2c4b2af1","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:26:58.000Z","msg":"而整個計劃只需要有足夠嘅人才，用幾千萬買下一個島嶼或者一個小漁村，建人工島工場，大量建島，可以找英國政府同澳洲傾，因為每個國家本土主義興起，好難有一個藉口比大量嘅人移民到澳洲。但如果你哋喺科技人才就唔同，容易傾好多，個Title係乜嘢大家可以商量，但呢個計劃係需要極大量嘅專才，一個舞台可以證明到你是這方面人才。"},{"pid":"45860c2f886c380aa4fefa293e4c5535b9560ca9","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:27:09.000Z","msg":"重新開始，只要有能力就有位上"},{"pid":"6cabbe4079c574bb0ba6d9060eb947e92bc2e4e1","tid":1499821,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:28:57.000Z","msg":"除非香港已經去到翻唔到身唧局面，如果唔係點都唔可以放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce6a08712e395509021bf06b3d4a5cde241c7474","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ad7aa2ecad475f5e527849099c24086f17923761","tid":1499821,"uid":277997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n我地要趕走佢地<br />\n唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:29:32.000Z","msg":"本計劃不是叫你放棄香港，你可以想像多了個香港人既地方，但有主權。"},{"pid":"d1f5488e09bf6f807ef8808a65738fbbf1ca6a24","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"6cabbe4079c574bb0ba6d9060eb947e92bc2e4e1","tid":1499821,"uid":89530,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:28:57.000Z","msg":"除非香港已經去到翻唔到身唧局面，如果唔係點都唔可以放棄香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:30:34.000Z","msg":"本計劃不是叫你放棄香港，你可以想像多了個香港人既地方，但有主權。"},{"pid":"218d14b8004f5d25cbf462a8f9e9f959babe34b9","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ad7aa2ecad475f5e527849099c24086f17923761","tid":1499821,"uid":277997,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:31.000Z","msg":"No<br />\n我地要趕走佢地<br />\n唔好放棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:33:33.000Z","msg":"香港沒有技術型製造業只有死路一條，另外香港太近中國完全比人滲透，無論你啲concept幾好，一切皆變成共狗啜乾香港嘅名目。"},{"pid":"80c45ded9c95b1b5bcc3e5d5fafbdec4ba6adcde","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:34:51.000Z","msg":"係海外成立一個真正嘅國家"},{"pid":"6a5a01a2fd5626552be8592a1bd4e6aa1d997b9e","tid":1499821,"uid":263068,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:40:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01ddbad3fdad13f5f039024aa264c1e0ad61f4b2","tid":1499821,"uid":282352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"如果夠人,一定ok ,再睇返佢個意念圖,個島面積可以一直加大,唔會有土地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一擔心,會唔會一個海潚滅國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bf685f19a2b79c31462ea1ce3da5b6736cc56be","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"01ddbad3fdad13f5f039024aa264c1e0ad61f4b2","tid":1499821,"uid":282352,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:47:52.000Z","msg":"如果夠人,一定ok ,再睇返佢個意念圖,個島面積可以一直加大,唔會有土地問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n唯一擔心,會唔會一個海潚滅國<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:48:41.000Z","msg":"新加坡人要去海外建國了，香港人一樣可以。<br />\n<br />\n大家如興趣可以加入FloatCityV出謀劃策。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fjoinchat%2FLERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ&d=iLyAB%2BOE6twWPMF9W2uC6oleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=66140c90\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/joinchat/LERSsRIsuYFLJ08KrMfqQQ</a>"},{"pid":"cf271810afaf4a745eaa4b8fbb441a9918836745","tid":1499821,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310bfd9b2ea50a42e98346844a043db7b773331f","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"其實我哋嘅目標係有<span style=\"color: red;\">主權</span>，有<span style=\"color: red;\">領土</span>。<br />\n我哋香港人唔可以再做二等公民，而家我哋係唔可以當兵，唔可以成為真正有實權既國家領導人。<br />\n<br />\n請大家推一下吧!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"52ab623cf1db2b6139f15546c00d57ec7634d09b","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cf271810afaf4a745eaa4b8fbb441a9918836745","tid":1499821,"uid":300554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"310bfd9b2ea50a42e98346844a043db7b773331f","tid":1499821,"uid":30561,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T01:25:28.000Z","msg":"其實我哋嘅目標係有<span style=\"color: red;\">主權</span>，有<span style=\"color: red;\">領土</span>。<br />\n我哋香港人唔可以再做二等公民，而家我哋係唔可以當兵，唔可以成為真正有實權既國家領導人。<br />\n<br />\n請大家推一下吧!"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:28:50.000Z","msg":"香港電影欠香港人一場革命<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1497679\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1497679</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/ZudLX07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZudLX07.jpg&h=5fb14145&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-24T02:29:49.000Z","msg":"本計劃不是叫你放棄香港，你可以想像多了個香港人既地方，但有主權。<br />\n<br />\n你只係多咗個國籍，多咗機會擁有自己嘅主權，將來會有自己的政府，更有自己的加密貨幣，如果喜歡澳洲的，可去澳洲買地/島 起人工浮島，而香港人居住偏遠地區三年以上可取得永居權。不需要做二等公民，我哋目標係發展教育，以及IT等等產業。"}]}